                            /* Count number of new messages and update number. */
                            function update_new_messages_count(){                                
                                var postData = {};
                                postData['form'] = 'search';
                                postData['action'] = 'messages_print_new';                                
                                var currentRequest = null;
                                currentRequest = $.ajax({
                                    type: 'POST',
                                    data: postData,
                                    url: 'ajax-handler.php',
                                    success: function (result) {
                                        var response = JSON.parse(result);                                        
                                        if(response){                                            
                                            if(response.status == 1){
                                                $('#new_messages_count').html(response.data.amount);                                                
                                                $('#new_messages_list').html(response.data.html);
                                                if(response.data.amount == 0){
                                                    $('#new_messages_count').slideUp(500);
                                                }else{
                                                    $('#new_messages_count').slideDown(500);
                                                }
                                            }else{                                            
                                                console.log(response.error);                                            
                                            }            
                                        }                                        
                                    },
                                    cache: false
                                });    
                            }
